===Noun===
'''bureau''' (''plural:'' '''bureaux''' or '''bureaus''')

# [[office]]
# [[desk]], usually with a cover and compartments for storing papers etc. located above the level of the writing surface rather than underneath
# (''US'') [[chest of drawers]] for clothes

